snippet.title: SNES Shanghai II: Dragon's Eye - Playthrough
snippet.description:
playthrough/longplay of the "Dragon's Eye" mode in Shanghai II on the Super Nintendo Entertainment System.

Shanghai II is a Mahjong puzzle game.

Relase:
1992 (SNES)

Developer:
Genki

Publisher:
Activision (USA, Europe)
HOT-B (Japan)


recorded with an Elgato Capture Card HD.


japanese:
スーパー上海ドラゴンズアイ
